Time":"2018-01-28T06:27:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-28T07:00:36.000Z","msg":"僱傭條例有&quot;即時解僱&rdquo;既概念<br />\n當僱員犯左嚴重過失或者相關既情況<br />\n僱主可以即時解僱佢<br />\n唔洗比通知期/代通知金 淨係要比人工<br />\n而呢樣野亦都適用於懷孕僱員<br />\n只要僱主justify到佢真係犯左嚴重過失就得"},{"pid":"c1d656e61af52f69625702a945357ed3fc6f67dd","tid":542989,"uid":167294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T11:29:10.000Z","msg":"parttime係咪都有有薪大假？"},{"pid":"5c5dbdf16271994b37feff9b8739becbb51baa83","tid":542989,"uid":1460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1d656e61af52f69625702a945357ed3fc6f67dd","tid":542989,"uid":167294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T11:29:10.000Z","msg":"parttime係咪都有有薪大假？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:56:34.000Z","msg":"僱傭條例冇分part time/full time<br />\n只係講「連續性合約」(418)<br />\n「連續性合約」係指連續比同一僱主請多過4星期<br />\n而每星期最少返18個鐘<br />\n只要你係418就有大假"},{"pid":"31eaab620fb9f91a895c33b347128a8cd77a8944","tid":542989,"uid":11217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T15:29:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c98eaae94258c242664ea328c62585b811f376ed","tid":542989,"uid":167294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c5dbdf16271994b37feff9b8739becbb51baa83","tid":542989,"uid":1460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1d656e61af52f69625702a945357ed3fc6f67dd","tid":542989,"uid":167294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T11:29:10.000Z","msg":"parttime係咪都有有薪大假？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T14:56:34.000Z","msg":"僱傭條例冇分part time/full time<br />\n只係講「連續性合約」(418)<br />\n「連續性合約」係指連續比同一僱主請多過4星期<br />\n而每星期最少返18個鐘<br />\n只要你係418就有大假"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-30T16:25:17.000Z","msg":"如果一年入面其中一個星期唔夠18粒鐘 僱主係咪有權一日都唔俾你？"},{"pid":"837b6d3671eb338cb742ecaedcaeb28deaf7e349","tid":542989,"uid":117082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:15:30.000Z","msg":"除左睇僱傭條例(香港法例第57章) 仲可以睇d咩了解下hr既條例，利申 想入行"}]}